# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# FF Arena — Frontend Environment Variables
# Set these in your Vercel / Netlify dashboard.  Do NOT commit real values.
# Copy to .env.local for local development overrides.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── API connection ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Full URL of your deployed Express backend (no trailing slash).
# Required when the frontend is hosted separately from the API.
# Leave blank when using the Vite dev-server proxy (local development).
# Example: https://ff-arena-api.onrender.com
VITE_API_URL=

# ─── Dev-server settings (set automatically by the Replit workflow) ───────────
# PORT=5000
# BASE_PATH=/
